fplot <- function(x){
 l <- FeaturePlot(epi, features = c(x)) +NoAxes()
ggsave(paste0("featurePlots/",x,".png"),plot = l,width = 3, height = 2.5, dpi = 300)
}
loxes <- c("LOX")

}

  graphList[[l]]<- a
  ggsave(filename = paste0("./violinplots/",l,".png"), plot = a, height = 3, width = 2, dpi=300)
}
